---
import ToolLayout from '../layouts/ToolLayout.astro';
const SITE = 'https://healthcalculation.com';
---

<ToolLayout
  title="About HealthCalculation — Accurate Health Calculators"
  description="Learn about HealthCalculation, our methodology, and the clinically validated formulas behind our free health and fitness calculators."
  canonical={`${SITE}/about`}
>
  <div style="max-width:780px;padding:32px 0 48px">

    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a><span>›</span><span>About</span>
    </nav>

    <h1>About HealthCalculation</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      We build free, accurate health calculators for everyday people who want to make
      informed decisions about their nutrition, fitness, and wellbeing.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Health information online is often buried behind sign-up walls or based on outdated science.
      HealthCalculation puts clinically validated formulas directly in your browser — instant, private,
      and free. No account required.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Methodology</h2>
    <p>
      Every calculator on this site is based on peer-reviewed research and recognized clinical
      guidelines. We cite our sources clearly on each tool page so you can verify the underlying
      science.
    </p>
    <ul style="padding-left:20px;margin:10px 0 16px;color:#374151;font-size:15px;line-height:2">
      <li><strong>Calorie / TDEE:</strong> Mifflin-St Jeor equation (Mifflin et al., <em>JADA</em> 1990; validated as most accurate for most adults by Frankenfield et al., <em>JADA</em> 2005)</li>
      <li><strong>BMI:</strong> WHO International standard (WHO, 2000)</li>
      <li><strong>Macros:</strong> USDA Dietary Guidelines 2020–2025 AMDR ranges</li>
      <li><strong>Sleep:</strong> American Academy of Sleep Medicine (AASM) 2015 consensus statement</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Medical Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>
      Results from our calculators are <strong>estimates for informational purposes only</strong>.
      They are not a substitute for professional medical advice. Always consult a qualified
      healthcare provider before making decisions about diet, exercise, or health.
    </p>
    <p>
      Individual metabolism varies. Estimates based on population-level formulas may not accurately
      reflect your personal needs.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Some pages on this site contain affiliate links. If you click a link and make a purchase,
      we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. We only recommend products and
      services we believe are genuinely helpful. Our editorial content and calculator results are
      never influenced by affiliate relationships.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Have a question, spotted an error, or want to suggest a new calculator?
      Email us at <a href="mailto:contact@healthcalculation.com">contact@healthcalculation.com</a>.
    </p>

  </div>
</ToolLayout>

<style>
  h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  h2 { font-size: 19px; font-weight: 700; margin: 28px 0 8px; }
  p  { font-size: 15px; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .lead { color: #6b7280; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; max-width: 620px; }
</style>
